    "API keys for Weather Underground and OpenWeatherMap are currently disabled. Weather data will use Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, or saved locations only." : {
      "comment" : "Status footer explaining disabled API keys.",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "API keys for Weather Underground and OpenWeatherMap are currently disabled. Weather data will use Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, or saved locations only."
          }
        },
        "an" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "API keys for Weather Underground and OpenWeatherMap are currently disabled. Weather data will use Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, or saved locations only."
          }
        },
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "مفاتيح API لـ Weather Underground و OpenWeatherMap معطلة حاليا. بيانات الطقس سوف تستخدم Apple Weather, Open-Meteo، أو المواقع المحفوظة فقط."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "API keys for Weather Underground and OpenWeatherMap are currently disabled. Weather data will use Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, or saved locations only."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Klávesy API pro počasí a OpenWeatherMap jsou momentálně zakázány. Data počasí budou používat pouze Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, nebo uložená umístění."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API-nøgler til Weather Underground og OpenWeatherMap er i øjeblikket deaktiveret. Vejrdata vil kun bruge Apple Weather, Open-Meteo eller gemte placeringer."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API-Schlüssel für Weather Underground und OpenWeatherMap sind derzeit deaktiviert. Wetterdaten verwenden nur Apple Weather, Open-Meteo oder gespeicherte Standorte."
          }
        },
        "el" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Τα κλειδιά API για το Weather Underground και το OpenWeatherMap είναι απενεργοποιημένα. Τα δεδομένα καιρού θα χρησιμοποιούν μόνο Apple Weather, Open-Meteo, ή αποθηκευμένες τοποθεσίες."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Las claves API para Weather Underground y OpenWeatherMap están actualmente deshabilitadas. Los datos del tiempo usarán el tiempo de Apple, Open-Meteo, o solo."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
