    "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card." : {
      "comment" : "Footer explaining card blur options.",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "an" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ضبابية الاختيار بين الرقيقة الفائقة، والمواد العادية. ضبط شفافية المواد كم تظهر الخلفية من خلال (60% يطابق المظاهر الأصلية). يرسم شريط الضوء كسر ضوء ناعم عبر البطاقة."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Rozostření se vybírá mezi ultra-tenkými, tenkými a normálními materiály. Materiálová průhlednost určuje, jak moc se zobrazuje pozadí (60% odpovídá původnímu vzhledu). Hrana zvýrazňuje slabé světlo protažené kartou."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Slør hakker mellem ultra-tynde, tynde og regelmæssige materialer. Materiale opacitet styrer hvor meget baggrunden viser (60% matcher det oprindelige udseende). Kant fremhæver tegner en blød lys feje hen over kortet."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Unschärfe zwischen ultradünnen, dünnen und regulären Materialien. Die Deckkraft der Materialien bestimmt, wie sehr der Hintergrund durch den Hintergrund zeigt (60% entspricht dem ursprünglichen Aussehen). Die Kantenhervorhebung zieht eine weiches Licht über die Karte."
          }
        },
        "el" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Το θόλωμα επιλέγει μεταξύ εξαιρετικά λεπτών, λεπτών και τακτικών υλικών. Η διαφάνεια των υλικών ελέγχει πόσο δείχνει το υπόβαθρο (60% ταιριάζει με την αρχική εμφάνιση). Το τονισμό της άκρης σχεδιάζει ένα μαλακό φως σάρωσης σε όλη την κάρτα."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Desenfoque escoge entre materiales ultra finos, finos y regulares. Material Opacity controla cuánto se muestra el fondo (60% coincide con la apariencia original)."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sumentaa välillä erittäin ohut, ohut, ja säännölliset materiaalit. Materiaali Läpinäkyvyys ohjaa, kuinka paljon tausta näyttää läpi (60 % vastaa alkuperäistä ulkonäköä). Edge korostus piirtää pehmeän kevyen pyyhkäisyn kortin yli."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Flou choisit entre des matériaux ultra-minces, minces et régulières. L'Opacité Matérielle contrôle combien l'arrière-plan affiche (60% correspond à l'apparence originale). La surbrillance du bord dessine un léger balayage sur la carte."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "hy" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sfocatura sceglie tra materiali ultra-sottili, sottili e regolari. Material Opacity controlla quanto lo sfondo mostra attraverso (60% corrisponde al look originale). L'evidenziazione bordo disegna una luce morbida attraverso la scheda."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "超薄型、薄型、通常の素材の間でぼかしをします。 マテリアルの不透明度はバックグラウンドがどのくらい表示されるかを制御します (60% は元の外観と一致します)。エッジのハイライトはカード全体に柔らかい光スイープを描きます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vervaag prikkels tussen ultra-dun, dun, en normale materialen. Materiaal Opaciteit bepaalt hoeveel de achtergrond door laat zien (60% komt overeen met de originele look). Het markeerpunt van het rand toont een zachte lichtbeweging over de kaart."
          }
        },
        "no" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Blur plukker mellom ultra-tynn, tynn og vanlige materialer. Material Opacity styrer hvor mye bakgrunnen viser gjennom (60% matcher den opprinnelige utseende). Edge fremhever tegner en myk lys sveip over kortet."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Rozmycie pikseli pomiędzy ultracienką, cienką i regularnymi materiałami. Przezroczystość materiału kontroluje ile pokazuje tło (60% odpowiada oryginalnemu wyglądu). Edge podświetla rysuje miękkie światło po całej karcie."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Desfoque escolhe entre materiais ultra-finos, finos e regulares. A Opacidade do Material controla o quanto o fundo é exibido (60% corresponde ao visual original). A função de destacar desenha uma luz suave através do cartão."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Desfoque escolhe entre materiais ultra-finos, finos e regulares. A Opacidade do Material controla o quanto o fundo é exibido (60% corresponde ao visual original). A função de destacar desenha uma luz suave através do cartão."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Blurează între materiale ultrarapide, subțiri și regulate. Materialul Opacitatea controlează cât de mult arată fundalul (60% se potrivește cu aspectul original). Edge evidențiază o breșă ușoară de pe card."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Размытие материалов между тонкими, тонкими и регулярными материалами. Непрозрачность материала управляет, сколько фона показывает (60% совпадает с исходным видом)."
          }
        },
        "sq" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "sr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Oskärpa plockar mellan ultra-tunna, tunna och vanliga material. Material Opacitet styr hur mycket bakgrunden visar genom (60% matchar det ursprungliga utseendet). Edge highlight drar ett mjukt ljus svep över kortet."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Розмиття між надтонкими, тонкими та регулярними матеріалами. Розмір тексту матеріалу контролює відображення фону (60% відповідно до оригінального вигляду). Підсвічення підсвічує м'яке світло на картці."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在超薄、薄薄和普通材料之间模糊不清。 素材不透明度控制背景显示多少(60%与原始外观相匹配)。边缘高亮绘制软灯光扫描。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Blur picks between ultra-thin, thin, and regular materials. Material Opacity controls how much the background shows through (60% matches the original look). Edge highlight draws a soft light sweep across the card."
          }
        }
      }
    },
