    "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish." : {
      "comment" : "Footer for experimental features.",
      "localizations" : {
        "af" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish."
          }
        },
        "an" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish."
          }
        },
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "هذه الميزات قيد التقدم. تمكينهم من تجربتهم، ثم تقديم الملاحظات حتى نعرف ما الذي سنصقله."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tyto funkce jsou v procesu. Povolte je vyzkoušet, poté napište zpětnou vazbu, abychom věděli, co má být vyleštěno."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Disse funktioner er works-in-progress. Aktivér dem for at afprøve dem, derefter fil feedback, så vi ved, hvad de skal polere."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese Funktionen sind im Gange. Aktivieren Sie sie, um sie auszuprobieren und dann Feedback zu hinterlassen, damit wir wissen, was zu polieren ist."
          }
        },
        "el" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Αυτά τα χαρακτηριστικά είναι εργασίες-σε-εξέλιξη. Ενεργοποιήστε τα για να τα δοκιμάσετε και στη συνέχεια τα σχόλια αρχείου, ώστε να ξέρουμε τι να γυαλίσουμε."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Estas características son trabajos en progreso. Habilitarlas para probarlas, luego archivar comentarios para que sepamos qué pulir."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nämä ominaisuudet ovat keskeneräisiä. Ota ne käyttöön kokeillaksesi niitä, sitten palautetta tiedostosta, jotta tiedämme mitä kiillottaa."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ces fonctionnalités sont en cours de progression. Activez-les pour les essayer, puis soumettez vos commentaires afin que nous sachions quoi polir."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "These features are works-in-progress. Enable them to try them out, then file feedback so we know what to polish."
          }
        },
        "hy" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
